32
00:02:48,719 --> 00:02:49,479
No way.

33
00:02:49,479 --> 00:02:51,520
She went to the hotel with Mr. Guan?

34
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:53,800
Didn't expect Miss Song to be so open.

35
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,280
Exactly.

36
00:02:54,719 --> 00:02:56,000
Song Qinian,

37
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:58,800
how many more surprises
will you give me tonight?

38
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,199
Everyone,

39
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,800
Miss Song

40
