41
00:03:07,439 --> 00:03:08,280
Please excuse us.

42
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:19,919
Mr. Shen,

43
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:22,319
didn't you see I was
catching up with Qinian?

44
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,599
Mr. Guan,

45
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,680
Song Qinian is my secretary.

46
00:03:26,479 --> 00:03:28,199
I hope you can keep
some distance from her.

47
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:30,280
Aren't you being a bit too meddlesome?

48
00:03:30,759 --> 00:03:32,159
This is between Qinian and me.

49
00:03:34,199 --> 00:03:35,000
Let's go.

50
00:04:09,719 --> 00:04:12,000
You really attract a lot of
attention, Song Qinian.

51
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,759
What's your relationship with him?

52
00:04:16,319 --> 00:04:17,519
(It's none of your business.)

53
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,560
How dare you, Song Qinian?

54
00:04:22,319 --> 00:04:23,959
(I don't have to explain myself to you.)

55
00:04:24,519 --> 00:04:26,759
(Just like you never explained
that I'm your wife.)

56
00:04:26,759 --> 00:04:27,680
(That's fair.)

57
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,920
Are you talking to me about fairness?

58
00:04:33,319 --> 00:04:34,120
Tell me

59
00:04:35,279 --> 00:04:37,000
how you seduce Mr. Guan.

60
00:04:37,639 --> 00:04:39,879
The way he looks at you makes me sick.

61
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,240
You flatter Mr. Liang

62
00:04:42,639 --> 00:04:44,000
and hook up with Mr. Guan.

63
00:04:44,319 --> 00:04:45,959
You are really quite something.

64
00:04:47,639 --> 00:04:48,759
(I didn't.)

65
00:04:49,879 --> 00:04:51,360
(You can ignore me.)

66
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,480
(But you can't slander me.)

67
00:04:53,759 --> 00:04:55,560
(Am I really that unimportant to you?)

68
00:04:56,736 --> 00:04:59,776
♪Fragment♪

69
00:05:06,816 --> 00:05:11,459
♪More than just regret♪

70
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:18,904
♪It's my presumptuousness,
after relying on the fearlessness♪

71
00:05:21,388 --> 00:05:27,396
♪It's my fault for taking your love
for granted♪

72
00:05:29,664 --> 00:05:34,805
♪I get used to your care♪

73
00:05:36,896 --> 00:05:43,312
♪Why the more I care,
the more I act indifferently♪

74
00:05:47,399 --> 00:05:49,000
Don't forget who you are,

75
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,480
Miss Song.

76
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,519
Before Qiutong wakes up,

77
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,759
you must stay by my side.

78
00:06:07,199 --> 00:06:10,040
Now, go back to the car immediately.

79
00:06:10,399 --> 00:06:12,279
Do not set foot in the private room.

80
00:06:16,879 --> 00:06:17,680
Be good.

81
00:06:56,279 --> 00:06:57,079
Miss Song.

82
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,240
Please take a seat.

83
00:06:59,759 --> 00:07:00,439
Sit over here.

84
00:07:01,279 --> 00:07:02,079
Be careful.

85
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,120
Miss Song,

86
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,879
it's your first time attending
such an event, right?

87
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:14,879
It's all

88
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:17,279
just for show.

89
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,439
Don't take it to heart.

90
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,079
(I know that.)

91
00:07:29,199 --> 00:07:30,480
(Thank you, Mr. Chen.)

92
00:07:31,759 --> 00:07:32,480
I

93
00:07:32,639 --> 00:07:34,839
just think you are about the same age
as my daughter.

94
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,279
By the way,

95
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:39,079
if you don't usually drink,

96
00:07:39,079 --> 00:07:40,319
after drinking so much at once,

97
00:07:40,639 --> 00:07:42,000
you need some hangover pills.

98
00:07:42,879 --> 00:07:44,600
I happen to have brought some today.

99
00:07:48,319 --> 00:07:48,800
Come on.

100
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,439
Your hand.

101
00:07:54,959 --> 00:07:56,040
Here, some water.

102
00:08:01,519 --> 00:08:02,040
Be careful.

103
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:02,759
Slow down.

104
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,480
(Thank you.)

105
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:20,000
Don't mention it.

106
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,439
Feeling better?

107
00:08:37,279 --> 00:08:38,279
Miss Song.

108
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:40,000
Miss Song, Miss Song.

109
00:08:46,159 --> 00:08:47,120
Mr. Shen,

110
00:08:47,559 --> 00:08:48,679
come on.

111
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:51,799
Take a seat.

112
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:53,200
Sorry.

113
00:08:54,639 --> 00:08:55,200
Mr. Liang,

114
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:56,879
if you have any requests,

115
00:08:56,879 --> 00:08:57,639
please tell me.

116
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:02,759
Business negotiations take time.

117
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,039
No rush.

118
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,720
Where is Miss Song?

119
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,240
She's drunk.

120
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,120
I told her to go home first.

121
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,519
You let her go alone?

122
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,879
What's it to you?

123
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,600
She's my secretary.

124
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,480
I'll be responsible for her safety.

125
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,960
You need to be responsible for too many.

126
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,279
Leave Qinian to me.

127
00:10:01,679 --> 00:10:03,000
I'm telling you today.

128
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,600
Qinian will be mine.

129
00:10:04,759 --> 00:10:06,600
Mr. Shen, you better recruit
a new secretary.

130
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:09,600
