133
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,799
Mr. Liang, I must take my leave.

134
00:10:20,064 --> 00:10:20,840
Mr. Liang.

135
00:10:24,559 --> 00:10:25,639
(Song Qinian,)

136
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:28,440
