a satisfactory answer.

142
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,879
Then, I'm leaving now.

143
00:10:51,639 --> 00:10:52,480
I'll see him out.

144
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:54,000
Be careful.

145
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:55,879
Take it easy.

146
00:10:55,879 --> 00:10:57,279
Right, be careful.

147
00:10:57,279 --> 00:10:58,120
Be careful.

148
00:10:59,679 --> 00:11:00,320
Mr. Shen,

149
00:11:00,679 --> 00:11:01,840
I'm impressed.

150
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:03,919
Be careful.

151
00:11:14,159 --> 00:11:15,919
